# IO.Swagger - ASP.NET Core 2.2 Server

API model to Saque e Pague transactions. The interessed partner should implement the desired operations so Saque e Pague may be able to communicate with it.

## Overview

This server was generated by the swagger-codegen project and customized by Saque e Pague Team.
By using the OpenAPI-Spec, you can easily generate a server stub.
This is an example of building a swagger-enabled server in dotnet core using the dotnet core framework. For more information, please visit http://www.saqueepague.com.br

## Requirements

Building the API backend application requires [dotnet core](https://dotnet.microsoft.com/download) to be installed.
